title: Alice in Wonderland - Collection (eBooks)
description:
Alice in Wonderland - Lewis Carroll - Collection (eBooks)


Biographies:
    Jenny Woolf - The Mystery of Lewis Carroll
    Robert Douglas-Fairhurst - The Story of Alice

Alice Books:
    Lewis Carroll - The Hunting of the Snark
    Lewis Carroll - The Nursery Alice
    Lewis Carroll (Haughton ed.) - Alice's Adventures in Wonderland and Through the Looking-Glass
    Lewis Carroll (Kelly ed.) - The Complete Alice in Wonderland
    Lewis Carroll (Woolf ed.) - Alice in Wonderland Illustrated
    Lewis Carroll (Woollcott ed.) - Complete Works
    Martin Gardner - The Annotated Alice - The Definitive Edition
    Tenniel engravings

Lewis Carroll's Mathematics Books:
    Lewis Carroll - Euclid and His Modern Rivals
    Lewis Carroll - Mathematical Recreations (Dover, 1958) (pdf)
    Lewis Carroll - Symbolic Logic (Potter, 1977) (pdf)
    Martin Gardner - Universe in a Handkerchief (Copernicus, 1996) (pdf)
    Lewis Carroll - The Game of Logic (Macmillan, 1886) (pdf)

mobi is compatible with Amazon Kindle, etc.
epub is compatible with Sony Reader, Cruz Reader, iPad, iPodTouch/iPhone, etc.

Free Calibre reader, for all O/S: http://www.calibre-ebook.com


Some repacks above, but also much new/reseeded material not otherwise available as torrents

If you're a fan of Lewis Carroll, you owe it to yourself to also check out Mike Batt's musical based on Carroll's "other" nonsense poem, "The Hunting of the Snark"
